In 2005 while working for the original McGill family business, The North Rocks Greenery, Jon id Jon took on his first Garden Maintenance customer armed with just a pair of secateurs. 13 years, hundreds of customers, some qualifications and a few trailers later Looking Up Landscapes was born.
